{"tid":1051060,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"DC《綠箭俠》宣布第八季完結 一代超級英雄落幕","createTime":"2019-03-07T09:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T06:21:09.000Z","uid":49391,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"52bb9ba416a281ca7eb1fdc3c1ecbe09af0ef5e9","tid":1051060,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T09:55:53.000Z","msg":"今日DC電視劇集《綠箭俠》的主演&ldquo;糖哥&rdquo;斯蒂芬&middot;阿梅爾通在推特上宣布，《綠箭俠》將在第八季正式完結，今年秋季播出的第八季將是他最後一次扮演綠箭俠奧利弗&middot;奎恩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZhHNOd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZhHNOd.jpg&h=9a0b348b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  &ldquo;扮演綠箭俠奧利弗&middot;奎恩是我人生中最精彩的職業經歷&hellip;&hellip;但你不可能永遠當一名英雄義警。《綠箭俠》完結季將在今年秋季到來。我有太多話想說&hellip;但現在，我只想對你們說一聲謝謝。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0dAqLzS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0dAqLzS.jpg&h=9eea6c48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《綠箭俠》第一季在2012年於CW電視台首播並大獲成功，從這一年開始，每年我們都會迎來綠箭俠與同伴們懲惡揚善的冒險故事，而我們能迎來這麼多CW電視台的DC劇集，《綠箭俠》的成功引領也功不可沒。電視劇第八季在今年2月初宣布續訂，糖哥今天除了宣布完結消息外，還透露完結季會有10集。"},{"pid":"50539cea918a8c5c6a0a21b6131c4ef2faf78b66","tid":1051060,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"其他果幾套點?仲有無聯動?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12669132defc6432dd5525dd4d864359bd7c7008","tid":1051060,"uid":3865,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T09:57:35.000Z","msg":"早啲完好撚過啦。。。拍到咁爛"},{"pid":"dbcbe76ab0918335a188a64457e2ad216db4412d","tid":1051060,"uid":52590,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"My name is Oliver........"},{"pid":"847df23ae58488206f87cb7f3be9d0e8df2da12d","tid":1051060,"uid":23363,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T09:59:33.000Z","msg":"頭兩季真係好震撼<br />\n之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f8ad11da6015a